snippet.title: Forgotten Hope 2 - 2.64 Compagnons Trailer
snippet.description:
Release trailer for the version 2.64 "Compagnons" launching 23rd of January 2024! 

Download and play Forgotten Hope 2 standalone for free from https://playfh2.net/ !

For more information regarding this new release, check out our homepage at  http://forgottenhope.warumdarum.de/ !
